  <summary>10/5/2011--Introduced.
Hardship Outlays to protect Mortgagee Equity Act of 2011 or the HOME Act of 2011 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow taxpayers to withdraw amounts from their tax-exempt pension and retirement plans, without incurring the 10%&#160;penalty otherwise imposed on such withdrawals,&#160;to make mortgage payments on their principal residences.</summary>
